          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer988246254" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11542619235542036338">Horrible horrible horrible, particularly the first two. Trust me, I&apos;m not saying this just for effect. They take &apos;dark&apos; to a whole new level - like staring down into a bottomless pit. Yet absolutely brilliant, more of a review later (maybe) once I&apos;ve recuperated.</span>
  <span id="freeText11542619235542036338" style="display:none">Horrible horrible horrible, particularly the first two. Trust me, I'm not saying this just for effect. They take 'dark' to a whole new level - like staring down into a bottomless pit. Yet absolutely brilliant, more of a review later (maybe) once I've recuperated.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11542619235542036338" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
